Currently using the ATMega32U4 microcontroller and have a board with several perripherials connected.

1) STR8676R Dot Matrix LCD
This is a small screen that I have paired with an ASCII bitmap in order to display text onto the screen.

Datasheet: https://www.lcd-module.de/eng/pdf/zubehoer/st7565r.pdf

2) 4 push buttons

3) 8 LEDs

4) 2.4 GHz meander antenna
